{"tid":1002083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地網紅主播禁情趣內衣　內地政協會議倡考試發牌","createTime":"2019-01-30T16:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T03:08:06.000Z","uid":66271,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a33af1ed2ed30c09bd445ec8804a269a2b9ba84b","tid":1002083,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2260000/2263471/KOL_thumb_20190130_E_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2260000%2F2263471%2FKOL_thumb_20190130_E_1024.jpg&h=cf5ab66f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地「網紅經濟」崛起，一些知名的網絡主播年收入數輒以百萬元起跳，甚至成為職業。惟內地政府近年加強對網上直播平台的監管。浙江就有省政協委員要求網紅考取相關執照。而湖北武漢昨亦實施網路直播規範，明訂女主播衣物不得過份暴露；未成年人不得單獨出鏡。<br />\n<br />\n當中包含對直播平台的主播和帳號監管、規範主播的衣裝要求及直播內容。女主播不得過份暴露、不能穿情趣制服、情趣內衣、透視裝、肉色緊身衣等。同時，未成年人若需在直播中單獨出鏡，需要提供監護人的身份證、戶口本照片、由監護人簽署的申請書等。直播平台在接到舉報後90秒內，需進行強制禁言、封號等處理。<br />\n<br />\n直播市場爆發式增長，截至去年4月，國內網紅的粉絲總人數達到5.88億。但不少主播衣著過份暴露，或賣弄色情。內地政府開始加強對主播的監控。湖北武漢28日推出中國首批網路直播標準&mdash;《網絡直播平台管理規範》與《網絡直播主播管理規範》，昨正式實施。<br />\n<br />\n而浙江亦有政協委員在剛召開的會議上提交《關於網紅職業素質培訓及持證上崗的提議》，要求省內的網紅必需接受職業培訓，並要通過考試取得相關執照，才能從事網絡直播。<br />\n<br />\n該建議指，職業培訓包括社會主義核心價值觀教育、相關法律法規普及、普通話語音訓練、表達技巧學習、形體塑造指導等，務求向大眾展示自信、健康的形象。培訓結束後，再統一考試發牌。另考慮建立網紅違規行為稽查機制，處罰違規網紅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家做雞都要考牌，搵食艱難<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba794b4bd86442520c66f368e7549f4d5818b3a","tid":1002083,"uid":59799,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:19:53.000Z","msg":"考官係一眾政協，試題係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f41c5c3bbb9d39c14bb95f6b02d8d776205938b","tid":1002083,"uid":197655,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:20:08.000Z","msg":"考官就係政協，試完咪發牌俾你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f3b33d09a1302f0c5e0b50f48efe8357b51a30","tid":1002083,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ba794b4bd86442520c66f368e7549f4d5818b3a","tid":1002083,"uid":59799,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:19:53.000Z","msg":"考官係一眾政協，試題係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:20:20.000Z","msg":"身體指導"},{"pid":"96983a3e00c9908364aeb2c4669ae8f6c11a73e1","tid":1002083,"uid":147198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:22:47.000Z","msg":"如果考英文試<br />\n<br />\n唔知會死幾多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb0e15bb9927c9ec065a44b8d8652845710f49c","tid":1002083,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3166cfba2157078c320fd35bfc440b88f19de2","tid":1002083,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:42:53.000Z","msg":"又要先陪瞓？"},{"pid":"a6f5cafa6ced3d176a9e2b8f7fb00af50efc438a","tid":1002083,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"96983a3e00c9908364aeb2c4669ae8f6c11a73e1","tid":1002083,"uid":147198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:22:47.000Z","msg":"如果考英文試<br />\n<br />\n唔知會死幾多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src